 Magnus and the destrons walked up to the  ship. It bright goldish color 
shined brightly. It was a half 3d sphere cut in half.(thats what it looks 
like) The destrons saw there where no visible ways of entrie. "Where  is the 
door."

 Magnus smiled"Right here." he placed his hand on the door and the scanner 
scanned his spark.. He made sure to enter all the knew sparks that would be 
entering. He watched as the door slided open as from nowhere. The destrons 
proceeded to install all the autoguns in the non visible compartment in the 
ship's outside hull. He then walked in. It was the chamber. Well his built 
version of the oracal chamber. There was an alter in the middle. He hooked up 
the shield generator. He pressed the button and dark sentinel came on-line.  
He put a self shield aroung the shield generator. It would only come off 
unless the bot answered three questions and also had the sprak signature of 
magnus. It would not be fooled by clones or any sort of duplication for it 
was always updateing its sensors to block anything of that type. So no one 
was getting to that shield generator. He pressed the button on the side wall 
and the alter carrying the shield generator slipped under the floor. and 
there was no visible compartment that may indicate it was there. He smiled 
and walked out of the chamber.
